data.description: Welcome to 3690 Riviera Ave! This home is an all brick ranch in Jackson Local School District! This ranch offers 1,508 sq ft of living space, including four bedrooms, and sits on half an acre. A two car garage, patio and shed are some more features of this property. Enter into the large living room with three good size windows for natural lighting. The living room opens to the dining room and into the kitchen that is fully equip with appliances, including a stainless steel gas range. The main bath has been updated with a tile shower and vanity with marble countertop. The basement is partially finished and would make for a great bonus room/living area. Dishwasher, water heater and gas range were all installed in 2019. Roof has 30 year shingles and was replaced in 2014. Master bedroom and ensuite have ben updated this year and as well as the chain-link fence in the back yard.
